{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Gale's default dialog that triggers whenever you speak to Gale in the game world. Covers a variety of topics that mostly react to Gale-related events that took place."
  },
  "dialogue": {
    "1": {
      "id": "1",
      "speaker": "Gale",
      "text": "Karsus was perhaps the most powerful wizard that ever lived. The-child-who-would-be-a-god, the elves called him.",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "16",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "4": {
          "id": "4",
          "speaker": "Gale",
          "text": "And he tried. With a spell of his own devising he endeavoured to usurp in one fell swoop the power of the goddess of magic.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "16",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "14": {
              "id": "14",
              "speaker": "Gale",
              "text": "Mystryl, she was called then. Imagine what it must have felt like. To be a god. To know yourself to be untouchable. To be mistaken.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "16",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "2": {
                  "id": "2",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "As Karsus aimed his spell at her, she began to unravel, and with her, the entire Weave.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "16",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "7": {
                      "id": "7",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "Too late did he realise what he had unleashed. It would have been the end of everything had not Mystryl sacrificed herself.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "16",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "19": {
                          "id": "19",
                          "speaker": "Gale",
                          "text": "The goddess of magic is all magic. By dying, the entire Weave was lost, and the spell that challenged a god failed.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "16",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "17": {
                              "id": "17",
                              "speaker": "Gale",
                              "text": "It was the end of Mystryl, the end of Karsus, and the end of an entire civilisation.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "16",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "22": {
                                  "id": "22",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "As the-child-who-would-be-a-god was turned to stone, his empire came crashing down around him. The floating cities of Netheril were no more.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "16",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "5": {
                                      "id": "5",
                                      "speaker": "Gale",
                                      "text": "An event that came to be known as Karsus' Folly.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "16",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "20": {
                                          "id": "20",
                                          "speaker": "Player",
                                          "text": "So at that moment in time, all magic was gone?",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [
                                            "CLERIC_MYSTRA",
                                            "PALADIN_MYSTRA",
                                            "WIZARD"
                                          ],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "16",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "13": {
                                              "id": "13",
                                              "speaker": "Gale",
                                              "text": "For a spell.",
                                              "context": "",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "",
                                              "is_end": false,
                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                              "children": {
                                                "9": {
                                                  "id": "9",
                                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                                  "text": "Mystryl was reborn as Mystra. Upon her return, the Weave returned with her.",
                                                  "context": "",
                                                  "checkflags": [],
                                                  "setflags": [],
                                                  "ruletags": [],
                                                  "approval": [],
                                                  "rolls": "",
                                                  "goto": "",
                                                  "link": "",
                                                  "is_end": false,
                                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                                  "children": {
                                                    "11": {
                                                      "id": "11",
                                                      "speaker": "Gale",
                                                      "text": "Now, so many centuries later, I tried to follow in the footsteps of Karsus, not to destroy Mystra, but to prove my love for her.",
                                                      "context": "",
                                                      "checkflags": [],
                                                      "setflags": [],
                                                      "ruletags": [],
                                                      "approval": [],
                                                      "rolls": "",
                                                      "goto": "",
                                                      "link": "",
                                                      "is_end": false,
                                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                                      "children": {
                                                        "21": {
                                                          "id": "21",
                                                          "speaker": "Gale",
                                                          "text": "I tried to control only a fraction of the magic that was unleashed that fateful day. I merely sought to return one tiny diamond to an imperfect crown.",
                                                          "context": "",
                                                          "checkflags": [],
                                                          "setflags": [],
                                                          "ruletags": [],
                                                          "approval": [],
                                                          "rolls": "",
                                                          "goto": "",
                                                          "link": "",
                                                          "is_end": false,
                                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                                          "children": {
                                                            "10": {
                                                              "id": "10",
                                                              "speaker": "Gale",
                                                              "text": "Gale's Folly one might call it. History. Repetition. It's the way things go.",
                                                              "context": "",
                                                              "checkflags": [],
                                                              "setflags": [],
                                                              "ruletags": [],
                                                              "approval": [],
                                                              "rolls": "",
                                                              "goto": "",
                                                              "link": "",
                                                              "is_end": true,
                                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                                              "children": {}
                                                            }
                                                          }
                                                        }
                                                      }
                                                    }
                                                  }
                                                }
                                              }
                                            }
                                          }
                                        },
                                        "3": {
                                          "id": "3",
                                          "speaker": "Player",
                                          "text": "Praise be that Mystryl was reborn as Mystra.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [
                                            "CLERIC_MYSTRA",
                                            "PALADIN_MYSTRA",
                                            "WIZARD"
                                          ],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "16",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "8": {
                                              "id": "8",
                                              "speaker": "Gale",
                                              "text": "Quite so.",
                                              "context": "",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "16",
                                              "is_end": false,
                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                              "children": {}
                                            }
                                          }
                                        },
                                        "18": {
                                          "id": "18",
                                          "speaker": "Player",
                                          "text": "Nothing good ever comes from mortals wanting to be gods.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "11",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "6": {
                                              "id": "6",
                                              "speaker": "Gale",
                                              "text": "Loving them has its side effects as well.",
                                              "context": "",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "",
                                              "is_end": false,
                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                              "children": {
                                                "16": {
                                                  "id": "16",
                                                  "speaker": "",
                                                  "text": "",
                                                  "context": "",
                                                  "checkflags": [],
                                                  "setflags": [],
                                                  "ruletags": [],
                                                  "approval": [],
                                                  "rolls": "",
                                                  "goto": "11",
                                                  "link": "",
                                                  "is_end": false,
                                                  "node_type": "jump",
                                                  "children": {}
                                                }
                                              }
                                            }
                                          }
                                        },
                                        "0": {
                                          "id": "0",
                                          "speaker": "Player",
                                          "text": "You have to admire the man's ambition. He very nearly succeeded.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "11",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "15": {
                                              "id": "15",
                                              "speaker": "Gale",
                                              "text": "If it takes the death of a god to stop you, I'd say your ambition has gotten somewhat out of hand.",
                                              "context": "",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "11",
                                              "is_end": false,
                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                              "children": {
                                                "12": {
                                                  "id": "12",
                                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                                  "text": "Not that I'm one to talk, of course.",
                                                  "context": "",
                                                  "checkflags": [],
                                                  "setflags": [],
                                                  "ruletags": [],
                                                  "approval": [],
                                                  "rolls": "",
                                                  "goto": "",
                                                  "link": "11",
                                                  "is_end": false,
                                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                                  "children": {}
                                                }
                                              }
                                            }
                                          }
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
